reply.question: 5. Does the app share data with third parties?

answer.full_answer: Yes, the app may share personal information with third parties when they perform services on behalf of Wellness Solutions.

reply.analysis: The privacy policy states that personal information may be disclosed to third parties when they provide services on behalf of Wellness Solutions. This indicates that data sharing with third parties is possible.
reply.reference: Personal information will only be disclosed for the above purposes. When third parties perform services on our behalf, we take reasonable steps to ensure the third party will protect your personal information in accordance with Australian privacy laws and in a manner consistent with this Privacy Policy. Personal information will not be used or disclosed for any other purposes without consent, except in exceptional circumstances where disclosure may be required by law or is necessary to protect WS, a member of the public or a threat to person’s health & safety. URL: https://www.wellnesssolutions.com.au/privacy-policy/
